    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_tb.00754.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                        <name type="place">Meltonsville, Alabama</name>
                    <date when="1875-04-26">April 26 1875</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Walt <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">Whitman</unclear></salute>
            </opener>

            <p>It is sometimes very hard to determine <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">one</unclear> 
                ought or ought not to do or say or <gap reason="illegible" extent="one or two words"/> I feel it rather 
                proper or necessary for me to <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">write</unclear> you 
                a letter now and do the best I can. Along with the 
                parcel of papers which you sent me after getting my <hi rend="underline">baby's letter</hi><ptr target="loc.01843_n1"/>
                I got the picture and the double column bill 
                previously sent me in the New Republic's regular issue (that is the matter of it) about Foreign Critics on an 
                American Poet. The last paragraph speaks of "<hi rend="underline">indigence</hi>", and I now write because of 
                that. Let me guess why you gave <hi rend="underline">authority to that statement</hi>&#8212;I think it 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">rather</unclear> 
                probable that you did so as a sort of <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">explanation</unclear>
                of the reason or a hint of the fact that <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> not able to offer the 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#me">little</unclear> <hi rend="underline">Walt</hi> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <hi rend="underline">present or keepsake</hi> as would be suited
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <hi rend="underline">dignity</hi> 
                or <hi rend="underline">exalted <unclear resp="#me" reason="illegible" cert="medium">worth</unclear></hi> the 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#me">part</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> 
                that light I could be<gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> of your <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/>
                wish you were too poor to <hi rend="underline">raise</hi> <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> pay 
                postage even on your <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#me">paper</unclear> If <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">you</unclear> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">know</unclear> me
                well, one of the <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>           
                <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_tb.00756.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> would be a remarkable <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/>,
                or <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="chars"/>sing <hi rend="underline">of riches</hi>, show, dress, or 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> not <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">described</unclear> 
                absolutely by good sense or <gap reason="illegible" extent="four words"/> kindness.</p>                                       
            <p>Leaving off that supposition, <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">it</unclear>
                <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#smb" cert="low">might</unclear> be taken <unclear reason="illegible" cert="high" resp="#me">that</unclear>
                you wanted me to post the bill as a sort of advertisement of your books. (When I 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">was at</unclear> "town" 
                (Guntersville) two weeks ago, I sent money to <hi rend="underline">Butts &amp; 
                Co.<ptr target="n0133c"/></hi> for a copy of Leaves of Grass to pass around among 
                the folks there as a specimen&#8212;hoping, yet scarcely expecting to do much in behalf of increased sales 
                of the same&#8212;</p>            
            <p>The third supposition must naturally be that my <hi rend="underline">real good-will</hi> is now tested. 
                I send a bill of money which is yours and you shall have a good deal more if you positively need it. 
                I have <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">yet</unclear> on hand <hi rend="underline">two 
                big bales of my cotton crop</hi> intended for spending money for the
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/>&#8212;sold <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">the</unclear>
                other of my crop (three more <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">big</unclear> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>) on one <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> credit to get 
                interest. Friend! <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> neither <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium"
                resp="#me">rich</unclear> nor "dog poor"&#8212;I am <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" 
                cert="medium" resp="#me">rich in</unclear> content</hi>&#8212;<gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> 
                a good farm, and <hi rend="underline">some<gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/></hi> 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#me">of</unclear> dollars <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">hands</unclear> of 
                relatives and friends <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <hi rend="underline">they will</hi>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> if I ever get to producing <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> to
                live on, <gap reason="illegible" quantity="4" unit="chars"/>self, wife, and little ones <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> horse"            
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc_tb.00757.jpg" type="recto"/>
                farm <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> money to pay taxes and <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>
                our <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> our tenants make for us all <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>
                grain <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> we lack only a little of being
                self-supporting <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> and need draw
                but lightly on our <hi rend="underline"><unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#aja">contingent</unclear> fund</hi>, 
                and when the crowd of <hi rend="underline">athletic</hi> <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#smb" cert="high">gymnastic</unclear> boys 
                shall grow a little larger I hope to <unclear reason="illegible"
                cert="low" resp="#me">clear</unclear> up more land and "make things happen"&#8212;Now, I can see clearly (as 
                I think) that friendship with or assistance to Walt Whitman, if he needs, is about the <hi rend="underline">best
                bid</hi> that any common man can make for immortality for himself and pleasure to his posterity&#8212;if 
                intellectual retrogression of mankind is ahead of us it will not be.</p>            
            <p>If the first supposition is correct, or the bill was <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">only</unclear> 
                accidentally put in the package of papers &amp; 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> us do this way&#8212;clearly you are not
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">rich</unclear> and I am not poor; to hurt&#8212;you 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">have</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">sending</unclear> me papers &amp;c 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">requesting</unclear> 
                an <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#me">stages</unclear>&#8212;if 
                you have means enough <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> or through kindness of immensely <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> 
                <unclear reason="illegible" resp="#smb" cert="medium">friends</unclear> or relatives) to live as <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#me">well as</unclear> you 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> if you are content to <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/>           
                <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc_tb.00758.jpg" type="verso"/>
                  
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> by a continuance of past <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/>
                I would <gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> to have you use the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#js">money</unclear> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> books, magazines or papers such as <hi rend="underline">you 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> like to read <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#al">most</unclear></hi> 
                and afterwards send to me. I don't care for scientific works 
                (<hi rend="underline">except new works about mental or moral Philosophy</hi>)&#8212;I 
                don't want political works, nor books of Poetry&#8212;I have not been such an enthusiast about Poetry as you
                might think, except that I have been <hi rend="underline">almost insane</hi> about 
                <hi rend="underline">yours</hi> because you have so well expressed "<hi rend="underline">my sentiments 
                exactly</hi>" (However, you don't convert me to "immortality"&#8212;I have been through 
                everything except <hi rend="underline">revival religion</hi> or positive 
                "knowledge of God") Walt! I think Nature made me for a 
                "Philosopher" and (<hi rend="underline">therefore</hi> skeptic",
                but <hi rend="underline">circumstances</hi> have made me <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> and
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> long time a believer <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#al">in</unclear>
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> of one
                sort or other. (Please don't <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> 
                other <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/>&#8212;<hi rend="underline">hunter come down</hi> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="six words"/> my <hi rend="underline">dilapidated dwelling</hi> 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two or three words"/>)</p> 
            <closer>
                <signed>John Newton Johnson <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/></signed>
                <address>
                    <addrLine><choice><abbr>Ala</abbr><expan>Alabama</expan></choice></addrLine>
                </address>
            </closer>
          <postscript><p><gap reason="illegible" extent="one word"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#nnk">for</unclear> 
                the past,<ptr target="loc.01843_n2"/> a rude but strong expression <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> your works have 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> possible desire to say "bully boy" 
                <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#me">know</unclear> 
                that <hi rend="underline">you heard me</hi>!! I think <gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> myself 
                hereafter by <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> Book always away from 
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="low" resp="#me">home</unclear>
         I think I would like to read <gap reason="illegible" extent="four words"/> 
                Life&#8212;have you seen it?&#8212;<gap reason="illegible" extent="three words"/> about <gap reason="illegible" extent="two words"/> 
